# Outline Skills

## Description

Operate Outline knowledge base - create, read, update, delete documents and collections, search content, manage users.

## Trigger

Use this skill when the user mentions:
- Outline
- Knowledge base operations
- Document management in Outline
- Collection management
- Wiki operations

## Usage

This skill provides Python scripts to interact with Outline API:

### Prerequisites

Set up your Outline API key:
```bash
export OUTLINE_API_KEY="ol_api_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx"
```

Or create `~/.claude/outline-config.json`:
```json
{
  "api_key": "ol_api_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx",
  "base_url": "https://app.getoutline.com/api"
}
```

### Common Operations

**Search Documents**
```bash
python scripts/search_ops.py "search query"
```

**Create Document**
```bash
python scripts/document_ops.py create --title "Title" --text "Content" --collection-id "id"
```

**List Collections**
```bash
python scripts/collection_ops.py list
```

